29  Kaae nelo apa olaiguanani loo Siraeli o Yehoshafat olaiguanani le Yuda Ramot-gilead. 
30  Nejoki olaiguanani loo Siraeli Yehoshafat, “Kalo nanu anapa pee alo olarrabal, kake nchopo iyie ilkilani linono le nkitoo.” Nelo olaiguanani loo Siraeli anapa nelo olarrabal. 
31  Neitanap apa olaiguanani le Siria lelo arikok le pokira tomoni uni oare loo ngarrin oo mbartan, ejo, “Emiaar oltung'ani kitok aashu oloti, kake olkitok loo Siraeli ake entaar.” 
32  Ore ake pee edol lelo akedok loo ngarrin oo mbartan Yehoshafat, nejo, “Esipa olaiguanani le Israel.” Kaae neibelekenya aarare ninye, neyietu Yehoshafat aishir. 
33  Ore ake pee edol lelo arikok loo ngarrin oo mbartan ajo mme olaiguanani loo Siraeli, neibelekenya aapuo te sujaroto enye. 
34  Kake eteyietuo oltung'ani obo enkawuo enye, neng'or olaiguanani loo Siraeli eripata e long'o enye, to lgoo. Ore enkaraki ina nejoki olaiguanani ilo arewani le ngarri enye oo mbartan, “Mbelekenyayu, iwaki matung'uai olarrabal, amu aatipikaki olbae.”


35  Neirowuaju olarrabal ina olong, neigarakino olaiguanani engarri enye eing'or enkalo oo ltung'ana le Siria. Ore pee eaku teipa neye ninye, ore osarge leina ng'oroto neiput oltiren leina garri oo mbartan. 
36  Ore etaa kedoyio enkolong neibulu olkiyioi enkop pooki, eji, “Shomo pooki tung'ani enkanasa enye, nelo pooki tung'ani enkop enye!”


37  Kaae neaku etua olaiguanani, neyauni ninye Samaria; nepuoi aanukaa ninye te Samaria. 
38  Nepuoi aaituku ina garri oo mbartan to lchorro le Samaria nemej ildiain ilo sarge lenye, ore nkituaak naaibor onyek neituku ate teilo sarge, te risioroto eilo rorei le Nkai apa oiroro ninye.


39  Ore nkulie kiaasin e Ahab, o nena pooki naataasa ninye, o ina aji oo lala loo lkanchaoni apa natesheta ninye, o nena anas pooki apa naatesheta ninye, neigero tiatua embuku oo ntepen oo laiguanak loo Siraeli. 
40  Kaae neirura Ahab neye anaa loo menye, neitoreisho Ahasia te rishata enye.

