41  Neiteru Yehoshafat olayioni le Asa aitore Yuda to lari liong'uan le enkitoria e Ahab olaiguanani loo Siraeli. 
42  Oloo larin tomoni uni o imiet apa Yehoshafat pee eiteru aitoreisho, neitoreisho ninye ilarin tikitam o imiet te Yerusalem. Ore apa enkarna e ng'otonye naa Asuba entito e Shilhi. 
43  Nerubare ninye orrekie le Asa Papaai lenye, eitu ninye eibelekenya apaash easata oo mbaa sidain te dukuya Olaitoriani. Ore ake eyia eitu eyai iwuejitin neeika, ore iltung'ana neitayu ilasarri nepej enkorropil te nena wuejitin neeika. 
44  Eitobira sii apa Yehoshafat osotua o laiguanani loo Siraeli.


45  Ore apa nkulie kiaasin e Yehoshafat, oina kidimata enye naitodolua, oina nashomo olarrabal, neigeroki tiatua embuku oo ntepen oo laiguanak le Yuda. 
46  Ore olpisiai le lelo ooibor onyek apa ootelekutua too nkolong'i e papaai lenye, neishie ninche teina kop. 
47  Meetae apa olaiguanani te Edom; olaiguanani oti ninye apa etegeluaki 
48  neitobir Yehoshafat imelin e Tarshish pee epuo Ofir aayau sahabu; kake eitu ninche epuo, amu eidaaitie nena melin te Esiong'eber. 
49  Neitoki Ahasia Olayioni le Ahab ajoki Yehoshafat, “Nchoo isinkan laainei epuo tenebo isinkan linono too melin.” Kake eitu enyorraa Yehoshafat. 
50  Neirrag Yehoshafat airura neye anaa loo menye, nenukari te nkurare oo loo menye te nkanasa e Daudi papaai lenye. Neitoreisho Yehoram olayioni lenye te rishata enye.

Olaiguanani loo Siraeli oji Ahasia


51  Neiteru Ahasia olayioni le Ahab aitoreisho te Isirael te Samaria to lari le tomon oopishana le nkitoria e Yehoshafat olaiguanani le Yuda, neitoreisho ninye ilarin oare te Israel. 
52  Etaasa apa ninye embae torrono too nkonyek o Laitoriani, nerubare orrekie le papaai lenye, o rrekie le ng'otonye, o rrekie le Yeroboam olayioni le Nebat, laa ninye apa oitapong'oyie Isiraeli metaasa eng'oki. 
53  Eisiaayia apa ninye Baal neserem ninye, neitagor Olaitoriani, Enkai e Israel, te pooki oitoi apa nataasa menye.

